title: Investigating The Cecil Hotel Mystery (Brandon Rogers)
itunes:author: Joe Vulpis & Ilya Feddy
itunes:summary:
Brandon Rogers is a massive comedy sketch YouTuber with over 5 million subscribers. We talk about working for the law firm that investigates the Cecil Hotel mystery, filming at Disneyland, and his new cartoon that's breaking ground.


Make sure to follow us @lightweightspod on insta and tell us who to have on next!
